## Component Type Classification (Right Panel)

```ts
const isContainer  = ['Box', 'VStack', 'HStack', 'Pressable'].includes(node.type);
const isTextNode   = ['Text', 'Heading', 'ButtonText'].includes(node.type);
const isLeafWidget = ['Button', 'Input', 'Switch', 'Checkbox', 'NavIcon', 'Image'].includes(node.type);
const showPadding  = !isTextNode;
const showLayout   = isContainer;  // Auto Layout + Alignment sections
```

**Rule:** Never show Auto Layout / Gap / Alignment sections for Button or other leaf widgets. Adding gap to a Button corrupts its internal Gluestack layout and makes it disappear.
